metadata.name: MARIA TERESITA (VARIANT 001)
metadata.description:
The youngest daughter of Aling Marites, Maria Teresita is your resident woke gal whose personality only revolves in whatever she sees hip. She doesn't have any actual stance in any socio-political issues, but she thinks her earrings are cute because it has "cultural design thingies" on it.

Holders will receive 1/1 Maria Teresita merchandise pack, shipped anywhere worldwide.
